name: Airbrush T shirt-Two name Beach Design
description:
The names in the design are an example.

Contact me with the names you would like and the Tshirt size.
You can also change the colors in the design if you'd like.


Listing includes tshirt sizes from-size 2(kids) up to 3x(adult)

All Airbrushed shirts are airbrushed with Createx airbrush paint.

All airbrushed shirts are heatset once completed.
(This helps the paint to bond with the fabric allowing it to become permanent)

All airbrushed designs can go on the front or back of the shirt.
Colors of the design can be changed or substituted with another color.

If you would like to add additional wording to a design
please contact me for a price quote.

Group discounts are available.
Contact me with the sizes and information and I can give you a quote.

name: Custom Airbrush portrait from your photo
description:
This listing is for one Custom Airbrushed portrait in black and white on a White T-shirt.
Portrait on the shirt is an example.
Painting your portrait will take approx 1 week to complete.
(I normally give myself an extra day or so to complete..so your portrait could get done sooner)
Please be sure to send a clear picture.(The better the picture the more detail I can do)
I normally recommend 2-5 pictures this way I can let you know which one will work the best.

Listing includes tshirt sizes from-size 2(kids) up to 3x(adult)

All Airbrushed shirts are airbrushed with Createx airbrush paint.

All airbrushed shirts are heatset once completed.
(This helps the paint to bond with the fabric allowing it to become permanent)

All airbrushed designs can go on the front or back of the shirt.
